/**
@mainpage @PROJECT_NAME@
@version @sqrl_version@
@author Adam Comley
@details libsqrl is a library implementing the <a href="https://www.grc.com/sqrl/sqrl.htm">SQRL Specification</a>.

@section about About
Visit <a href="https://sqrlid.com">SQRLid</a> for more information, development status, and new releases.

@section platforms Supported Platforms
This implementation is intended to work on multiple platforms.  Tested platforms include:
- Mac OS X (Tested on 10.11.4 64 bit)
- Linux (Tested on Ubuntu 14.04.4 LTS, 64 bit)

With minimal work, this implementation should run on iOS, Windows, and Android as well.  We have not had an opportunity to test these platforms yet.

@section using Using libsqrl
- Read the <a href="https://sqrlid.com/libsqrl">libsqrl documentation</a>
- View the <a href="https://github.com/Novators/libsqrl">source code</a>

Installation and Testing:
First, get the source code and make your build directory:

@code
git clone https://github.com/Novators/libsqrl.git
cd libsqrl
mkdir build
cd build
@endcode

To generate an Xcode project:

@code
cmake -G Xcode ..
@endcode

Or, to use Unix makefiles:

@code
cmake ..
make
make test
@endcode

